Or even cooler but mor difficult a hip step up( I’ve only seen a few on YouTube) it would definitely give u that sketchy flare you like.

It’s a traditional step up but the take off is kind of twisted left or right and you rotate while traveling up to land on a flat that’s at a different angle than end of the ramp.

and so Mrs. bike hacks stays, happy you could line the sides with flowers .
